      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im sorry to bother u but im kinda freaking out. i feel like my neighbors are doing something to me. like, whenever i'm in my living room there's this weird low hum or vibration and it just makes me feel super angry and anxious for no reason. i dont think its just in my head. have u ever heard of people using sound to mess with others?",
