      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just \"feelings\" though. its like a physical pressure in my chest. i looked them up and people talk about research on acoustic weaponry and how certain frequencies can actually trigger fight or flight responses. it feels way too targeted to be accidental. do u think it's actually possible for someone to use something like that in a residential area?",
