    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've already seen a doctor and they said everything is fine with me, so i know it's not just a medical thing. it's the timing that's so weird... every time i try to relax or when i'm alone, it starts up. it feels like they're trying to keep me on edge so i can't focus. if they are using some kind of specialized frequency, would it even show up on a normal sound meter or something? i feel like if i can't prove it, they're just gonna keep doing it.",
